node.text:
We are announcing Community Challenges. Here comes the first one: «Standard Bearer».
— Drop to any map in the Capture mode.
— Carry the enemy flag for 30 seconds outside the bases on a map.
— Win the match
Additional mission:
— Kill 3+ enemies
⠀
Rewards:
Top 10 participant will get 300 gems, plus 1000 coins if additional mission is complete.
⠀
How to participate:
1. Record your successful game
2. Upload the video to YouTube. It MUST have the following name «Pixel Gun 3D Standard Bearer Challenge»
3. Max one entry per player.
4. We will stop submissions on Monday, August 12.
***
In this video you can see how one of the devs, desperaterussian, completes this challenge.
Aaaand, yeah, remember, those, who complete the mission faster than others will definitely receive the prize.
Good luck!
⠀
#PixelGun3D #pg3d #pixelgun

node.text:
UPDATE 21.6 is out now on iOS 🍏 Settle on a journey and unravel the mystery of the sinister sands! ☠️☠️
⠀
👆DOWNLOAD via the link in Bio👆
⠀
NEW
🛕New Competition system. Precise matchmaking, new leaderboard, awesome rewards, and more...
🛕Egyptian Season. Find the sacred scarab before the wrath of the ancient gods strikes the world!
🛕Shiny Ra Set. Become an immortal! Punish your enemies with the power of the sun
🛕Sinister Gods Bundle. Anubis and Khepri summoned the army of the dead!
🛕Cursed Pharaoh Van. Death is just the beginning
🛕Scarab Temple Map. Danger lurks in the ominous tomb
⠀
FREE PLAY
🐫Excavations event zone. Who knows what mysteries are hidden in the ancient ruins
🐫More decorations in some areas and buildings
⠀
IMPROVEMENTS
⛏️New Lobby. Only the essential features now!
⛏️Settings tab rework
⛏️Balance Changes and other improvements
⠀
#pg3d #pixelgun #PixelGun3D

No need to thank us 😇

node.text:
We've got a HUGE announcement for you today. We've made our first Dev Update! 🤩
⠀
What's that? 🤔
Well, this is the format in which we'll tell you a little bit about our plans for the future and show you some upcoming new features.
⠀
Follow the LINK in STORIES to see the Pixel Gun 3D Dev Update#1

❗Making progress on the investigation❗

We found four more suspects in this tangled case. You can see their faces in the picture 🦹‍♂️

We are confident that we uncovered all the members of the gang. All that remains is to unravel the complete code sequence 🕵️

You can send the code directly to the BLOQ Investigations department by filling out the Google Form. You can find the LINK on our latest Facebook post or in our Stories.

💎Don't forget that 10 random people who send the correct code will receive a reward of 1000 GEMS💎
